Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.42,0:01:08.34,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.34,0:01:09.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.33,0:01:10.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.56,0:01:11.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.26,0:01:16.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? You're spilling your rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.52,0:01:18.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.44,0:01:20.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.35,0:01:22.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking about my exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.94,0:01:24.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.40,0:01:26.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They start tomorrow, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.02,0:01:26.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:28.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.84,0:01:30.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Already?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.64,0:01:32.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.37,0:01:38.52,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to do tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.52,0:01:41.74,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,when I meet Yano-san, Yoshida-san and Kazehaya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.67,0:01:48.45,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.45,0:01:50.37,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,we've got exams now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.37,0:01:53.08,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's sitting in attendance order.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.08,0:01:55.93,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's in my usual seat?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.73,0:01:58.38,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.38,0:02:01.50,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,She isn't avoiding my seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.50,0:02:04.30,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,After all the rumors that went around because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.56,0:02:15.57,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Those three never avoided me. They were never afraid of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.87,0:02:20.37,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,They've always been nice to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.26,0:02:26.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.40,0:02:30.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, you're in Sadako's seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.09,0:02:33.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.82,0:02:41.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally she greets everyone even if it creeps them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.25,0:02:44.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She just went straight to her seat. She didn't even look at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:45.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.39,0:02:47.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.21,0:02:51.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's not being herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.83,0:02:57.25,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Being here in this different seat,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.25,0:03:00.15,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like that other arrangement was never there to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.04,0:03:04.62,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Like it has never been that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:08.53,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels distant, like it was all a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.03,0:03:11.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.60,0:03:16.22,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I really wanted to be useful, not a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.11,0:03:23.58,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,But I still haven't fixed the misunderstandings about Yano-san and Yoshida-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.58,0:03:29.64,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I find the people spreading the rumors and make them stop,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:35.20,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,if I stay here, I'm going to end up hurting them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.20,0:03:37.15,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Such kind people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.20,0:03:40.96,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I may be able to stop the rumors,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.96,0:03:48.09,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't know how to make them feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.09,0:03:51.94,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm going to go back to what it was like,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.94,0:03:54.23,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,before I got used to being around them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.23,0:03:57.79,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,That has to be the best thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.59,0:04:01.55,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Yoshida-san used those notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:05.22,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope they were at least a bit helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:11.63,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano-san, I can tell a scary story now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.63,0:04:14.27,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted you to be the first to hear it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:17.02,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,but I guess that won't happen anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.37,0:04:24.50,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya-kun, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:35.66,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so happy whenever you were around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.37,0:04:38.79,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always longed for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.79,0:04:41.84,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always looked up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.29,0:04:47.09,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how I used to live with being alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.58,0:04:54.77,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already discovered what it feels like to be kind, to receive kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:59.36,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how to go back. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:02.18,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,How did I bear being alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.18,0:05:04.29,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,How did I never lose my mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.36,0:05:10.33,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I've forgotten it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.51,0:05:13.92,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,All of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.80,0:05:37.44,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,The first day of summer,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:42.47,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya-kun was here waiting just the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.47,0:05:45.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.00,0:05:48.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't hate me, why are you avoiding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.78,0:05:56.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:02.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.32,0:06:07.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say what I don't even understand myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.03,0:06:08.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.35,0:06:11.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry if I ruined your reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.41,0:06:11.30,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.86,0:06:13.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.40,0:06:15.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speak properly so that I can understand you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.20,0:06:22.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to ruin your reputation if I stay around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.52,0:06:23.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reputation?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:24.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.41,0:06:26.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.03,0:06:27.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rumors?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.98,0:06:30.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reputations, rumors...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:33.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about how {\i1}I{\i0}{\fscx50} {\fscx100} feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.20,0:06:36.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not something for you to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:39.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's for me to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:46.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.87,0:06:49.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I want to talk to you, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.29,0:06:52.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I didn't want to, I wouldn't be talking to you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:06:58.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:05.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only Kuronuma I know is the one that I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.75,0:07:10.53,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:15.74,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,People like Yano-san, Yoshida-san and Kazehaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.61,0:07:19.57,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.51,0:07:27.50,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,to care for people and to be cared for.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.25,0:07:33.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feeling better?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:37.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.63,0:07:39.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:43.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.07,0:07:51.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep this, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:57.06,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I was feeling so hopeless until just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.06,0:07:58.20,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:08:04.25,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever Kazehaya-kun laughs, I feel at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.25,0:08:07.39,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,As if my heart becomes untangled.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.23,0:08:13.22,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,The only Kuronuma I know is the one that I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:15.10,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.10,0:08:18.06,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like I was being told that I could be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.95,0:08:20.12,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.53,0:08:22.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:26.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were being awkward because of the rumors about Yano and Yoshida.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.55,0:08:30.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if it were the other way around?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.58,0:08:39.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Yano or I avoided you thinking we'd ruin your reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.74,0:08:43.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.41,0:08:47.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd want to stay together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.07,0:08:52.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That might be how they're feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.70,0:08:56.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's all about how the other person feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.17,0:08:59.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how they feel,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.88,0:09:03.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they might get worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:07.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I was worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.60,0:09:09.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.88,0:09:10.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.86,0:09:13.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:16.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.68,0:09:21.50,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,People have refused to let me come near,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.50,0:09:24.22,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't think anyone's ever refused to let me avoid them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:31.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I've been thinking about it all in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:34.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wouldn't know unless I asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.75,0:09:38.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, they wouldn't know unless I told them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.34,0:09:41.07,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to tell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.07,0:09:46.03,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I want Yano-san and Yoshida-san to listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.03,0:09:47.70,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,To my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:51.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You already have someone you can talk to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.96,0:09:58.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to try talking to Yoshida-san and Yano-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.96,0:10:04.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just as classmates,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.74,0:10:07.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but as friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:12.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm going to try my best to be their friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.29,0:10:15.87,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.87,0:10:16.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.51,0:10:22.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.55,0:10:35.39,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,His simple words, his smiles... they always nudge me forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.03,0:10:46.52,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it, Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.90,0:10:48.91,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.41,0:10:54.90,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya-kun, I'm going to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.81,0:10:58.60,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going for it. Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.22,0:11:09.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.12,0:11:11.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home and start studying or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.54,0:11:14.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was about to go to the library to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.33,0:11:17.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're more hard-working than you look.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:22.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:25.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hadn't shown up back then—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.51,0:11:27.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:30.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if I hadn't show up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.57,0:11:32.62,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,If he hadn't show up...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.51,0:11:36.33,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I would have heard what Sadako was saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.70,0:11:39.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:42.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you, don't go blaming me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.72,0:11:45.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever it is you're talking about,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:48.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're not going to get anywhere until you stop blaming other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.43,0:11:52.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to run into a lot of awful situations in your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.14,0:11:55.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, it's up to you to do something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.96,0:11:57.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.12,0:12:00.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.12,0:12:03.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You figure it out yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:08.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, you better have given those print-outs to Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.47,0:12:11.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I burned them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:13.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:16.03,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go blaming me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:18.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.65,0:12:23.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the last person I want to hear that from.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.91,0:12:31.14,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the book Sadako was reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:34.81,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.35,0:12:42.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.98,0:12:46.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why all Japanese horror stories?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:48.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.62,0:12:53.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might as well take advantage of that appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.99,0:12:58.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.60,0:13:01.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an eager student.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.91,0:13:09.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.23,0:13:13.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to cheer you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.63,0:13:18.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it. I'm not upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:22.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since you were a kid you'd cause trouble and get kicked out
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.35,0:13:25.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then you'd sit out here all upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.31,0:13:26.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.73,0:13:28.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, did you run here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:32.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Pin's practice menu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.03,0:13:36.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not upset about the rumors about you being a delinquent, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:38.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those rumors are no match for my thick skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.65,0:13:39.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.41,0:13:44.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not too smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:47.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.64,0:13:50.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Sadako really Sadako or is she Dark-Sadako?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.55,0:13:52.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, I don't know either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.55,0:13:54.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's like,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.76,0:13:55.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,those rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.96,0:13:58.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said it was Sadako spreading them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.96,0:14:01.05,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How would she ever even spread rumors?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.05,0:14:02.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By talking to herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:07.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There'd be rumors about her talking to herself if she did that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.78,0:14:10.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but who else would she be talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.70,0:14:15.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, that's so true!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.97,0:14:16.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Simpleton.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.35,0:14:22.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, she was talking to some girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.13,0:14:26.05,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something about us not being friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:29.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she doesn't like me or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:32.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I think she's avoiding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.38,0:14:36.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you mean, “sorry,” Sadako?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.84,0:14:40.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you just say you liked me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:42.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess she doesn't really like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.49,0:14:48.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what, do you think she hates me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.07,0:14:49.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think she was taking advantage of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.51,0:14:50.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.61,0:14:53.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe she doesn't even care.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.35,0:14:58.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:15:01.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something? Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.09,0:15:02.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.58,0:15:05.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just ask her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:09.05,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cheer you up if she says she doesn't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.05,0:15:09.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.94,0:15:11.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.95,0:15:26.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell, “something else”?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.50,0:15:31.07,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It was really easy to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:34.66,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,She made this for me, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:43.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my god Sadako, you suck at drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:56.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who goes through so much trouble for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:04.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chizu, can you come out right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.01,0:16:08.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was the exam?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:13.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only got the parts that Sadako helped me with.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.62,0:16:14.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.90,0:16:20.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako hasn't even smiled since things turned awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:25.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako seemed so happy lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:29.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She laughed when we were studying for the exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.67,0:16:32.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She did. That was surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:40.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.93,0:16:44.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'd gotten used to being avoided.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.38,0:16:47.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was normal for her, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.10,0:16:51.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that a bit sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.21,0:16:52.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so nice too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:56.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I couldn't just leave her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.71,0:16:59.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.03,0:17:01.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You get used to the attitudes around you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.72,0:17:03.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it gets hard to know how people are feeling,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.78,0:17:06.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or even how you're feeling yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.55,0:17:10.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sort of know what that's like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.29,0:17:14.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why when she laughed,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.16,0:17:16.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.02,0:17:20.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you were thinking all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.06,0:17:23.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry dammit, it's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.25,0:17:29.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't realize you were thinking the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.14,0:17:34.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I thought I knew Sadako pretty well,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.14,0:17:38.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I guess we were getting upset because we only thought we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.19,0:17:42.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then again, there are things we don't know about each other too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.56,0:17:50.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano-chin, there's something important that we haven't talked to Sadako about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:56.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako doesn't know that we feel this way either, does she?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.50,0:18:01.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What she meant by “sorry,”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.98,0:18:04.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or “not friends,”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.11,0:18:07.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or the rest of what she was saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.96,0:18:14.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think she would have said?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.25,0:18:20.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think we'd ever get involved with her at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.99,0:18:24.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we're thinking about her constantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.19,0:18:26.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.09,0:18:29.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much does she need to frustrate us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:32.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look how much we think about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.25,0:18:37.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must really love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.49,0:18:42.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We said we weren't sure if we were friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.29,0:18:46.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but really, we're totally friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.32,0:18:52.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, look at how much we think about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.68,0:18:58.56,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't know how someone else is feeling unless I ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.56,0:19:02.85,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Other people won't know how I'm feeling unless I tell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.85,0:19:07.14,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to know because we don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.14,0:19:09.99,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I can think that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.99,0:19:13.96,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I can feel that way,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.96,0:19:19.97,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,to have met people that make me think that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.67,0:19:26.73,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,When I see them:
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.73,0:19:29.31,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,“let me talk to you...”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:33.08,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,But they'll probably be studying for the exam during the break.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.08,0:19:33.99,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,After school?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.99,0:19:37.04,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll probably be studying then too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.01,0:19:43.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hear something from over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.34,0:19:44.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:48.55,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm nervous, but I don't mind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.55,0:19:51.30,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,You already have someone you can talk to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.30,0:19:52.93,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I have someone I can talk to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.81,0:19:57.08,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I have people that'll listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.08,0:20:00.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit, I'm really screwed for the exam today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.21,0:20:02.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.34,0:20:02.85,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.85,0:20:05.17,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I spent too much time here thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.87,0:20:07.59,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, remember that rumor about Sadako?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.59,0:20:10.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About Yano and Yoshida backing her up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.39,0:20:14.14,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,The rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.14,0:20:16.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, apparently —
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:18.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:29.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano-san and Yoshida-san aren't backing me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.45,0:20:33.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:37.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano-san and Yoshida-san are nice people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.46,0:20:38.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.98,0:20:41.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“Nice people”? What the hell is she talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.82,0:20:43.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she wants to talk to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.63,0:20:45.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's sorta glaring at us, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.65,0:20:48.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what I always look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.04,0:20:50.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, Yano-san and Yoshida—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.57,0:20:54.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.59,0:20:57.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, Yoshida and Yano, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.48,0:20:59.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.69,0:21:02.78,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,The criminal and the slut.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.27,0:22:28.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mistakes to be fixed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.51,0:22:29.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feelings unyielding
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.12,0:22:33.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Friends
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.70,0:22:35.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
